maintaining the attack going.} (16. Nxd4 {dismantles the attacking mechanism,
allowing} fxe6 17. Bg5 (17. Bxe6+ $2 {With the knight away from f3, this allows
} Kh8 $1 $17) 17... Qd6 $11) 16... Bxf3 {The rook seems to be hanging now...}
17. Rxh6 $1 {Consequent and strong.} gxh6 (17... Bd5 {fails to parry the
