{[#] What should White do now?} 21. d5 $1 {Of course. Everything is ready for
it.} e5 (21... exd5 22. Bxf6 gxf6 23. Qg4+ $18) 22. a4 {Playing solidly.} ({
I rejected} 22. Ng4 Nxg4 23. hxg4 {on account of} b5 {even though White
maintains an edge with} 24. Be4 bxc4 25. Qxc4 $16) (22. Qd3 $16) 22... g6 (
22... a6 23. Bc3 $16 Ba3 (23... b5 $2 24. Ba5 Rd7 25. Bf5) 24. Qd3 g6 (24...
Bxc1 25. Ng4 Ba3 26. Nxf6+ gxf6 27. Bd2 Bc5 28. Bh6 $18) 25. Bxe5 Bxc1 26. Bxf6
Bxe3 27. fxe3 $18) 23. Ng4 Nxg4 24. hxg4 Qc8 25. g5 $16 {White has finally
achieved a dream position, but at this point in the game I was getting short
of time already. Marin,M (2543)-Jianu,V (2532) Olanesti 2018 (½-½, 50)} *

