{How should Black react to the central break?} 19... c4 $1 {It is esential to
defend the a2-g8 diagonal.} (19... dxe4 $2 {allows} 20. Nxg6 $18) 20. Qc2 dxe4
21. Nxe4 Nxe4 22. Bxe4 Bxe4 23. Qxe4 Bf6 $11 {Black's position is suddenly all
right. Foisor,O (2420)-Boensch,U (2475) Leipzig 1986 (0-1, 42)} *

